Package: plotibcs
Title: Create IBCS-Compliant Vertical Waterfall Charts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Owen", "Price", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A data-driven interface for producing charts that closely
    mimic IBCS templates. Users decide data grouping and some minimal
    formatting, but most formatting is pre-defined on purpose.
